# 🔌 Wiring Diagram - ESP32 Air Quality Monitoring System

---

## 📡 ESP32 #1 - SENDER (Pengirim Data Sensor)

### Komponen:
- ESP32-WROOM-32
- Sharp GP2Y1010AU0F (Sensor Debu PM2.5)
- DHT22 (Sensor Suhu & Kelembaban)

---

### GP2Y1010AU0F → ESP32 #1

| Sensor (Kabel) | ESP32 Pin |
|----------------|-----------|
| LED (putih) | GPIO2 |
| VO (hitam) | GPIO34 (ADC) |
| GND | GND |
| VCC | 5V / VIN |

### DHT22 → ESP32 #1

| Sensor (Kabel) | ESP32 Pin |
|----------------|-----------|
| DATA (kuning) | GPIO26 |
| VCC (merah) | 3.3V |
| GND (hitam) | GND |

### UART Serial2 → ESP32 #2

| ESP32 #1 | ESP32 #2 |
|----------|----------|
| GPIO1 (TX) | GPIO3 (RX) |
| GPIO3 (RX) | GPIO1 (TX) |
| GND | GND |

---

## 📡 ESP32 #2 - RECEIVER (Penerima Data & Upload Cloud)

### Komponen:
- ESP32-WROOM-32

### UART Serial2 ← ESP32 #1

| ESP32 #2 | ESP32 #1 |
|----------|----------|
| GPIO1 (TX) | GPIO3 (RX) |
| GPIO3 (RX) | GPIO1 (TX) |
| GND | GND |

---

## 🔄 Alur Komunikasi Data

ESP32 #1 (SENDER)
- Baca sensor debu → PM2.5
- Baca sensor DHT22 → suhu & kelembaban
- Format data: `pm25,suhu,hum`
- Kirim via UART Serial2

⬇️ *(TX: GPIO1 → RX: GPIO3)*

ESP32 #2 (RECEIVER)
- Terima data dari Serial2
- Parse CSV
- Upload via WiFi/HTTP

⬇️ *(HTTP API)*

ThingSpeak Cloud
- Simpan data time series
- Visualisasi grafik
- Dataset untuk prediksi

---

## 📌 Pin Summary

### ESP32 #1 (Sender)
| Pin | Fungsi |
|-----|--------|
| GPIO2 | LED sensor debu |
| GPIO34 | VO sensor debu (ADC) |
| GPIO26 | DATA DHT22 |
| GPIO1 | TX Serial2 |
| GPIO3 | RX Serial2 |
| 5V/VIN | VCC sensor debu |
| 3.3V | VCC DHT22 |
| GND | Ground semua komponen |

### ESP32 #2 (Receiver)
| Pin | Fungsi |
|-----|--------|
| GPIO1 | TX Serial2 |
| GPIO3 | RX Serial2 |
| GND | Ground (harus tersambung ke ESP32 #1) |

---

## ⚠️ Catatan Penting

1. GP2Y1010AU0F pakai 5V — jangan sambung ke 3.3V
2. DHT22 pakai 3.3V
3. GND kedua ESP32 harus terhubung (untuk referensi sinyal UART)
4. TX → RX, RX → TX (cross-connection UART)
5. Pastikan baud rate kedua ESP32 sama: 115200
